  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2309280/extras/4e101af41e023b01fec758f54b18d8c6.avif?t=1682627533\" width=620 height=260 /></span><br><br>Mini Star Cafe is a Simple relaxing game that expands the store by making and selling Coffee & bread.<br><br><strong>Features</strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Simple making system<br></li><li> 100 Bread Recipes<br></li><li> 100 Coffee Recipes<br></li><li> Upgrades and floor expansion elements<br></li><li> Beautiful and intensely colored visuals<br></li><li> Comfortable and relaxing OST<br></li><li> 10~12 hours of playtime</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2309280/extras/70414de752def55aefc1af8eca15f096.avif?t=1682627533\" width=620 height=260 /></span>",
